{"tid":490711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前貧乳AV女優秀「全裸膠帶裝」　粉絲硬了","createTime":"2017-12-06T01:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T02:34:31.000Z","uid":34498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a8952c6f3754da0e26e7ad307a68d50e8b740a","tid":490711,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:08:27.000Z","msg":"日本前AV女優木村都那(木村つな)今年2月引退後，轉型成視覺型藝人，在Cosplay界大放光彩，日前她分享近來再度引起話題的「全裸膠帶裝」，讓粉絲好興奮。<br />\n<br />\n木村都那引退後改名霧宮天(霧宮てん)轉型為藝人，而4日她在《推特》分享近來引起話題的「全裸膠帶裝」，粉絲看到A罩杯的她做出這種高露出度的造型，留言「鎖骨、胸部、屁股的平衡超級讚」、「皮膚保養的真好」、「看得我心跳加速阿」、「難道又要引起風潮了嗎」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_bad7ccf2df2b6afbe3f459ccfe7594fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_bad7ccf2df2b6afbe3f459ccfe7594fd.jpg&h=af44059c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n前貧乳AV女優秀「裸體膠帶裝」　粉絲硬了。翻攝自霧宮てん推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_5f7001eb52813770dbe9b3161162bd9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_5f7001eb52813770dbe9b3161162bd9f.jpg&h=dd847f50&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n年也曾流行過。翻攝自AGOシャン☆&rlm;推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_6927b60a2a2e9c9a5ae3aa1a49a6b4ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_6927b60a2a2e9c9a5ae3aa1a49a6b4ca.jpg&h=22a07751&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n前年也曾流行過。翻攝自AGOシャン☆&rlm;推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_6c8817df7874eab8d161126e72950aee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_6c8817df7874eab8d161126e72950aee.jpg&h=6aacb8d2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n前年也曾流行過。翻攝自AGOシャン☆&rlm;推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_db10f5f6ddb046febc841e8b768f4dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_db10f5f6ddb046febc841e8b768f4dbb.jpg&h=440f7430&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n近來又引起流行。翻攝自りみる推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_edf46c7e44542c0b95edfa1e44d804bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_edf46c7e44542c0b95edfa1e44d804bd.jpg&h=8061c998&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n近來又引起流行。翻攝自りみる推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_2cd0053f871fa77cee380526148c0322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_2cd0053f871fa77cee380526148c0322.jpg&h=4b630ded&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n近來又引起流行。翻攝自りみる推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_48b631691980650480d6f3cfe10e3a8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_48b631691980650480d6f3cfe10e3a8a.jpg&h=7dfcc12c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n近來又引起流行。翻攝自なのあん&rlm;推特<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171205/640_191f208a0c6cf4b3333fa011988a4741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171205%2F640_191f208a0c6cf4b3333fa011988a4741.jpg&h=3d4a68bc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n近來又引起流行。翻攝自なのあん&rlm;推特<br />\n <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20171205/1253381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171205%2F1253381&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1565cc41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20171205%2F1253381&h=39c81abb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/